      "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
      "body" : "Note that creating the JAR by double-clicking on the jardesc file and then clicking Finish, you&#39;ll be prompted to save the jardesc again, as it was originally created with the Save Description flag set. Easiest way around this is to manually edit it, and change <code>saveDescription=&quot;true&quot;</code> to <code>saveDescription=&quot;false&quot;</code>."
