    "body" : "<p>Creating a builder launcher is an issue since 2 projects cannot have the same external tool build name. Each name has to be unique. I am currently facing this issue to automate my build and copy the JAR to an external location.</p>\n\n<p>I am using IBM's Zip Builder, but that is just a help but not doing the real.</p>\n\n<p>People can try using IBM ZIP Creation plugin.\n<a href=\"http://www.ibm.com/developerworks/websphere/library/techarticles/0112_deboer/deboer2.html#download\" rel=\"nofollow\">http://www.ibm.com/developerworks/websphere/library/techarticles/0112_deboer/deboer2.html#download</a></p>\n"
